Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.games.states

Class TakeMarbleState

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.games.states.TakeMarbleState
All Implemented Interfaces:
GameState
public class TakeMarbleState
extends java.lang.Object
implements GameState
TakeMarbleState is one of game states. In this state current player can only send use marble or switch messages, any other message will be discarded. This state saves the chosen marbles to avoid player uses wrong ones.
